  "text": "Animals. Wild-type and Syt IV knockout mice (Syt4 -/-) and Sprague-Dawley rats were anesthetized and decapitated according to procedures approved by the Animal Care and Use Committee of the University of Wisconsin. Syt IV knockout mice [CITATION_1] were provided by H. Herschman (University of California Los Angeles). Genotype was confirmed by PCR of tail-clip DNA.",
